Question.Subject: Paypal shipping label creator charged me and messed up my label!!?
Question.Content: Hi I used paypal's shipping label creator and I paidfor and printed out my label, however I realized that instead of Seattle, it said Seatac. Assuming this was my fault I remade the label, making sure to spell it correctly, however, When I purchased the label again, It once again changed Seattle to Seatac. Why is it doing this?? Is there any way to get my money back for the labels?
Question.ChosenAnswer: Best way to get this resolved is to contact PayPal: https://www.paypal.com/us/contactus

Answer.Content: Best way to get this resolved is to contact PayPal: https://www.paypal.com/us/contactus
